{"tid":1578373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實民主及人權法可以過到, 真係唔係陳云功勞,而係一名默默地勾結外國勢力既香港人","createTime":"2019-09-18T06:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T06:25:08.000Z","uid":31637,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"67134ba02e7b745ca8c69f72308023eb40ab5e32","tid":1578373,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:08:44.000Z","msg":"個民主及人權法, 其中一個制裁就係凍結共黨海外資產<br />\n呢個Idea, 係由某一班連登仔諗出黎 (我都係其中之一個)<br />\n而真係將連登仔Idea提交比美國, 係一名一直默默地勾結外國勢力既香港人<br />\n果個肯撚定唔係陳云, 如果陳云成功勾結外國勢力, 以佢d痴撚線既idea, 共產黨一早倒撚左台<br />\n所以功勞肯定唔係歸陳云<br />\n但陳云同陳云班支持者出心出力係真既 (正正係因為唔可以直接同侵侵班底聯繫,怕比人出賣,先要咁出心出力)"},{"pid":"01c59976e230958a6f48f4508c06bdf5b76cfcc0","tid":1578373,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa76070429255dd7dbd058ba28e5279abba5e9a5","tid":1578373,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"請大家盡量俾多D建議或公布一下各地行動資料<br />\n[統籌/文宣] 9.29 Global Anti Chinazi Rally<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahDQchU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahDQchU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網上：</span><br />\nTwitter,<br />\n每晚9點係twitter 開關於Chinazi既Tweet 再加以下hashtag<br />\n#929GlobalAntiChinaziRally<br />\n#AntiChinazi<br />\n個人建議